<HEADLINE>
<P>
FAMILY PLANNING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Child abuse, abandonment, school dropouts, teen-age pregnancies, gangs, drugs 
and prisons are so often the results of being "unwanted children." This is a 
well-documented fact. Working mostly with Hispanic women in a family planning 
clinic, I am hearing the recent and desperate concern of "what will we do 
without the help of this clinic." 
</P>
<P>
I strongly plead with the governor to restore these much-needed funds for 
family planning, which ultimately benefit us all. 
</P>
<P>
EVA L. BARCIA 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
