Inner Turf Course in 2:18 3/5 to pick up his second victory in five starts this 
year. Coeur de Lion, with 121 and Jean Cruguet, was 1 1/2 lengths ahead of Pay 
the Butler, 116 and Robbie Davis. 
</P>
